imageDescription: A lone figure walks confidently down a neon-lit city street, back turned to the camera, ignoring the whispers and blurred faces of the crowd. They're bathed in a warm inner light, headphones on, with a determined expression. Graffiti art style, vibrant colors, and a sense of liberation.
